snippet.title: Katamarayudu (HD) - Pawan Kalyan Blockbuster Action Comedy Romantic Movie | Shruti Haasan
snippet.description:
Katamarayudu and his brothers settle the issues in a violent way. Katamarayudu hates love and marriage as that sours their relationship. Though being stubborn, Katamaarayudu ' s brothers fall in love. When they plan to marry his brother may reject them. For that they plan to get him married to Avantika. Finally Katamaarayudu and Avantika fall in love. When Avantika gets to know about his violent way of dealing, she starts hating him. Katamarayudu start mending in non violent ways. But when he gets to know that Avantika 's family is going to annihilated it's up to the duty of Katamaarayudu and his brothers to protect her family.

Movie:- Katamarayudu
Starcast:- Pawan Kalyan, Shruti Haasan, Nassar, Ali, Siva Balaji
Directed by:- Kishore Kumar Pardasani
Music by:- Anup Rubens

-------------------

Abandoned as a newborn by her own heartless mother and raised by her resilient maasi, Shruti, Mannat grows up to be a passionate and ambitious chef, unaware of her mysterious origins. Her journey intertwines with that of Vikrant, a successful buisnessman (restaurateur), as they bond over their love for cooking amidst the vibrant backdrop of Mumbai's chawls and elite culinary spaces. Mannat‚Äôs biological mother is none other than Aishwarya, a wealthy and manipulative woman determined to keep her secrets buried who is also Mannat's boss at Mezbaani where she works as a junior chef. Life takes a dramatic turn when Mannat discovers Shruti is not her biological mother, propelling her on a desperate quest to save Shruti‚Äôs life by finding her real mother for a liver transplant. Amidst these revelations, Mannat finds her strongest support in Vikrant, the prince charming of her life, who stands by her side, offering unwavering encouragement as she navigates the challenges life throws her way. As Mannat‚Äôs rising career, Shruti‚Äôs failing health, and the revelations of a hidden past collide, Mannat faces a whirlwind of love, betrayal, and self-discovery. Will her dreams and resilience help her overcome the storm, or will the weight of her past keep her from achieving her destiny?

snippet.title: Simran's Fire Speech on Stage üî•üíØ | "I Do Not Deserve This" üò° - Simran | JFW Movie Awards 2025
snippet.description:
Simran has completed 30 years of being an actress in the industry and has gained respect and love from all over the world! At the JFW Movie Awards 2025, a grand celebration took place as Simran was honoured by more than 10 actresses such as Keerthy Suresh, Krithi Shetty, Parvathy Thiruvothu, Amala Paul, Sri Gouri Priya, Sriya Reddy, Nikhila VImal, Grace Antony, Swasika and Dushara! Simran's speech was bold as she talks about how she received an unnecessary text from a co-star and that she rather do "Aunty" roles than roles that do not mean anything! 

Simran recently did a cameo in the blockbuster hit "Good Bad Ugly" and was praised for her brilliant performance and her iconic dance was used in the movie with Ajith Kumar!

Watch the video now and let us know your feedback in the comments section below!

I was the first guest at Yuvraj Singh‚Äôs first-ever restaurant, Koca, in Gurugram ‚Äî and it wasn‚Äôt just about delicious food. This episode is packed with heartwarming, inspiring, and unheard stories straight from Yuvraj‚Äôs life.

I sat down for an intimate conversation with Yuvraj Singh and his mother, Shabnam Singh, where she opened up like never before. From adorable childhood memories of Yuvi, his rebellious streak, and the challenges of raising a champion, to their family‚Äôs struggle during his battle with cancer ‚Äî she shared it all.

We also spoke about Yuvraj‚Äôs journey to cricket stardom, his equation with his father Yograj Singh, her parenting style as a single mother, and for the first time, how she was introduced to her daughter-in-law Hazel Keech. It‚Äôs a candid, emotional and joyful episode you don‚Äôt want to miss!

And of course, you‚Äôll get an exclusive tour of Koca, where Yuvi takes me through his favorite dishes and the story behind launching his dream restaurant.

From the secret behind her legendary Kadhi Chawal, to Yuvraj‚Äôs most emotional cricket moments, his battle with cancer, love life with Hazel Keech and becoming a dad at 40, nothing is off the table!


Hit play, join us for this special brunch, and don‚Äôt forget to like, comment, and subscribe!

snippet.title: Koi Naa | Bhool Chuk Maaf | Rajkummar Rao, Wamiqa Gabbi | Tanishk, Irshad, Shreya, Harnoor, Gifty
snippet.description:
Sang tere rehna khayal banke,
Aati mujhe duji tarqeeb koi na!
 
Presenting the first song release ‚ÄòKoi Naa‚Äô from ‚ÄòBhool Chuk Maaf‚Äô, featuring Rajkummar Rao and Wamiqa Gabbi! Composed by Tanishk Bagchi and Gifty, it is sung by Harnoor and Shreya Ghoshal and penned by Irshad Kamil. Perfect to dedicate to someone who‚Äôs a romantic, let this speak the words of your heart to that special someone!
 
#KoiNaa #ShreyaGhoshal #Harnoor #TanishkBagchi #Gifty #irshadKamil #RajkummarRao #WamiqaGabbi #BhoolChukMaaf
 
Song credits:
Title : Koi Naa
Singers : Harnoor & Shreya Ghoshal
Composers : Tanishk Bagchi & Gifty
Music Production : Tanishk Bagchi & Ganesh Waghela
Lyricist : Irshad Kamil
Language : Hindi
Mix Master : Eric Pillai @ Future sound of Bombay
Assistant Mix Engineer : Michael Edwin Pillai
Original Punjabi Music & Lyrics : Gifty
Original Song Licensed by Jatt Life Studios
 
Maddock Films presents #BhoolChukMaaf
In cinemas on 9th May
Cast: Rajkummar Rao, Wamiqa Gabbi, Sanjay Mishra, Seema Pahwa, Zakir Hussain, Raghubir Yadav, Ishtiyak Khan, Anubha Fatehpuria
Produced By: Dinesh Vijan
Directed By: Karan Sharma
Co-Producers: Sharada Karki Jalota
Music By: Tanishk Bagchi
Background Score: Ketan Sodha
Story Screenplay & Dialogues By: Karan Sharma
Director Of Photography: Sudeep Chatterjee
Lyrics: Irshad Kamil
Director of Choreography: Vijay A Ganguly
 
Lyrics:

Yaara mere dil ke kareeb koi na
Tere siva apna naseeb koi na
Sang tere rehna khayal banke
Aati mujhe duji tarqeeb koi na
 
Kehta hai tujhko haseen aaina
Tujh mein hi rehta hai leen aaina
Bolo isey mujhko jalaya na kare
Lena maine tujhse ye chheen aaina
 
Mujhse hi sun le tareef apni
Shaadi wali milti lakeer apni
Teri meri duniya basegi jis mein
Aane wali jaldi tareekh apni

Tu to mere surmey jaisa
Tu to mere sapne jaisa
Akhiyon Mein
Rakhna hai
Sabse chhupa ke tujhko
Chupke se
Marzi se
Chaahungi  tujhko

Yaara mere dil ke kareeb koi na
Tere siva apna naseeb koi na
Sang tere rehna khayal banke
Aati mujhe duji tarqeeb koi na

Dilon ki ameeri mein gareeb koi na
Ashiqon se badh ke ajeeb koi na
Aankhein milein jab tab Jaan pe baney
Ishqey se oonchi to saleeb koi na
 
(Tere jaisa ik mera Yaar aaina
Chadhti jawani ka shingaar aaina
Dekho mujhe kitna guroor ho gaya
Leke aayin mujhpe nikhaar aaina)

Chura le mujhe ab Sajjana tu saara
Jawani tere naam kar di maine yaara
Laga ke tujhe honth se apne dekhun
Kahan se tu m meetha kahan se khaara

Paaniyon pe behte chiraag jaisi tu
Mehke gulaabon ke hai baag jaisi tu
Thandi hoti akkhiyann tujhe dekh ke
Chhooney se to lagti hai aag jaisi tu
 
Yaara mere dil ke kareeb koi na
Tere siva apna naseeb koi na
Sang tere rehna khayal banke
Aati mujhe duji tarqeeb koi na

Tera mera ek jaisa haal ho gaya
Dooriyon mein rahna mohaal ho gaya
Le ke aaja jaldi. Baraat maahiya
Rang meri menhdi ka laal ho gaya
 
Tu to mere surmey jaisa
Tu to mere sapne jaisa
Akhiyon Mein
Rakhna hai
Sabse chhupa ke tujhko
Chupke se
Marzi se
Chaahungi  tujhko

Yaara mere dil ke kareeb koi na
Tere siva apna naseeb koi na
Sang tere rehna khayal banke
Aati mujhe duji tarqeeb koi na

Main tere pe mar gayi sajna re
Tu samjha na
Ishq se main bhar gayi sajna re
Tu samjha na
Tere aage peechhe ghoomti phirun
Piye bina hi main jhoomti phirun
Tere saaye ko bhi choomti phirun
Meri jaan
Tujhpe nisaar sajna

Yaara mere dil ke kareeb koi na
Tere siva apna naseeb koi na
Sang tere rehna khayal banke
Aati mujhe duji tarqeeb koi na

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. snippet.title: Superman | Superman Day - Behind The Scenes Look
snippet.description:
We‚Äôre just getting started. #Superman - Only in Theaters and @imax, July 11 #LookUp #SupermanDay 

‚ÄúSuperman,‚Äù DC Studios‚Äô first feature film to hit the big screen, is set to soar into theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures. In his signature style, James Gunn takes on the original superhero in the newly imagined DC universe with a singular blend of epic action, humor and heart, delivering a Superman who‚Äôs driven by compassion and an inherent belief in the goodness of humankind.

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and Gunn are producing the film, which Gunn directs from his own screenplay, based on characters from DC, Superman created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.

The film stars David Corenswet (‚ÄúTwisters,‚Äù ‚ÄúHollywood‚Äù) in the dual role of Superman/Clark Kent, Rachel Brosnahan (‚ÄúThe Marvelous Mrs. Maisel‚Äù) as Lois Lane and Nicholas Hoult (the ‚ÄúX-Men‚Äù movies, ‚ÄúJuror #2‚Äù) as Lex Luthor. The film also stars Edi Gathegi (‚ÄúFor All Mankind‚Äù), Anthony Carrigan (‚ÄúBarry,‚Äù ‚ÄúGotham‚Äù), Nathan Fillion (the ‚ÄúGuardians of the Galaxy‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Suicide Squad‚Äù), Isabela Merced (‚ÄúAlien Romulus‚Äù), Skyler Gisondo (‚ÄúLicorice Pizza,‚Äù ‚ÄúBooksmart‚Äù), Sara Sampaio (‚ÄúAt Midnight‚Äù), Mar√≠a Gabriela de Far√≠a (‚ÄúThe Moodys‚Äù),
Wendell Pierce (‚ÄúSelma,‚Äù ‚ÄúTom Clancy‚Äôs Jack Ryan‚Äù), Alan Tudyk (‚ÄúAndor‚Äù), Pruitt Taylor Vince (‚ÄúBird Box‚Äù) and Neva Howell (‚ÄúGreedy People‚Äù).

‚ÄúSuperman‚Äù is executive produced by Nikolas Korda, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars Winther. Behind the camera, Gunn is joined by frequent collaborators, including director of photography Henry Braham, production designer Beth Mickle, costume designer Judianna Makovsky and composer John Murphy, along with composer David Fleming (‚ÄúThe Last of Us‚Äù), editors William Hoy (‚ÄúThe Batman‚Äù), Jason Ballantine (the ‚ÄúIT‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Flash‚Äù) and Craig Alpert (‚ÄúDeadpool 2,‚Äù ‚ÄúBlue Beetle‚Äù).

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment/The Safran Company Production, A James Gunn Film, ‚ÄúSuperman,‚Äù which will be in theaters and IMAX¬Æ nationwide on July 11, 2025, and internationally beginning 9 July 2025, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.title: Pyaro Vrindavan (Official Video) | Indresh Upadhyay Ji | B Praak | Mir Desai | Kripa Records
snippet.description:

Let the music transport you to the sacred lanes of Vrindavan, where every note echoes with bhakti and every frame radiates spiritual grace. This is more than just a song ‚Äî it‚Äôs a journey into the heart of devotion.
